{"TopicId":188951,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Settings reset at every game launch 1.8","CreatedByName":"Jahnus","CreatedById":200798,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-16T23:22:41Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jahnus","CreatedById":200798,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-16T23:22:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EHi guys,\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:rgb(248,249,250);color:rgb(34,34,34);text-align:left;\u0022\u003EWith a clean installation version 1.8, without mods, The settings reset at each launch of the game. I tried to delete the .cfg file,\u00A0nothing works. When I return the game in 1.7.3 beta in steam, no problem. The game keeps my settings, but when I go back to 1.8 settings reset each time ...\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:rgb(248,249,250);color:rgb(34,34,34);text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Serenity","CreatedById":179192,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T01:25:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223688424\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571268161\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200798\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jahnus\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Jahnus said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EHi guys,\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\