 tried to delete the .cfg file,\u00A0nothing works. When I return the game in 1.7.3 beta in steam, no problem. The game keeps my settings, but when I go back to 1.8 settings reset each time ...\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:rgb(248,249,250);color:rgb(34,34,34);text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame problem.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have\u00A0have steam cloud saving enabled.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd each time a update my setting, the game quit the \u0022full screen mode\u0022. I have to use\u00A0alt \u002B enter to restore it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jahnus","CreatedById":200798,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T07:37:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223688490\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571275542\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179192\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Boyster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Boyster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you have steam cloud saving enabled?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you use controllers?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI copied the KSP folder on the desk, to put steam out of action. \u00A0but same way ...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo controller use in KSP, I deleted my xbox 360 controller from windows, same way...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jamaniek","CreatedById":195349,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T11:03:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExactly same problem here. I reinstalled the game few times, disabled steam cloud saving but still no dice.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BezKartuza","CreatedById":200469,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T18:37:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe problem is the same (Steam version). delete all modifications. No manipulations help! Reinstalled several times. Deleted the folder with the rest of the game. Nothing helps.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy system:\u003Cbr\u003E\nWindows 10\u003Cbr\u003E\nProcessor - AMD Ryzen 5 2600\u003Cbr\u003E\nRAM - 16 GB\u003Cbr\u003E\nVideo card - GeForce GTX 1050 2 GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jojo5144","CreatedById":176773,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T18:38:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsame problem for me \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u00A0 . \u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BezKartuza","CreatedById":200469,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T18:53:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://bugs.kerbalspaceprogram.com/issues/23909\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://bugs.kerbalspaceprogram.com/issues/23909\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T19:39:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223688946\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571338402\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200469\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022BezKartuza\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n46 minutes ago, BezKartuza said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022i