atedDateTime":"2019-10-17T19:52:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223688987\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571341836\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200469\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022BezKartuza\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, BezKartuza said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan title=\u0022\u0022\u003EYes I know.\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan title=\u0022\u0022\u003EBut I want to play in my native language.\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan title=\u0022\u0022\u003EIf the game did not have support for the Russian language, I would not buy it.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is why it is called a work around. Also that was meant for other people looking at this thread, not you.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BezKartuza","CreatedById":200469,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T20:00:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223688993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571341973\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MechBFP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, MechBFP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is why it is called a work around. Also that was meant for other people looking at this thread, not you.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I have the right to say my word. I paid my money and I want everything to work. In my opinion this is a normal desire. And I think I\u0027m not the only one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I\u0027m damn angry at developers today!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T20:01:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223688997\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571342453\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200469\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022BezKartuza\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, BezKartuza said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I have the right to say my word. I paid my money and I want everything to work. In my opinion this is a normal desire. And I think I\u0027m not the only one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I\u0027m damn angry at developers today!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUh huh. You will notice\u00A0I didn\u2019t say otherwise.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BezKartuza","CreatedById":200469,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T20:04:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223688999\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571342496\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MechBFP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, MechBFP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUh huh. You will notice\u00A0I didn\u2019t say otherwise.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s right. I\u0027m just out of sorts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vandest","CreatedById":122250,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-18T00:52:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello guys,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe work around is about Regional Format of Windows. You can still play in your language if you want.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThis will change your date and hour format in Windows only.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo do that:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nOpen your Windows tab (completely left in the taskbar)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOpen Settings (\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan title=\u0022\u0022\u003Enotched wheel)\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan title=\u0022\u0022\u003EClick on \u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETime \u0026amp; Language\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan title=\u0022\u0022\u003EClick on \u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERegion\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nUnder the \u201C\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERegional format\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u201D section, use the drop-down menu to set it to \u0022\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EEnglish (United States)\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u0022\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nOfcourse, the words in bold and underline will be in your language ...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope this will help someone while waiting for the fix.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-10-18T01:57:21Z\u0022 title=\u002210/18/2019 01:57  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 18, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Vandest\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jahnus","CreatedById":200798,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-18T08:25:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223689184\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571359963\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022122250\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vandest\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Vandest said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello guys,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe work around is about Regional Format of Windows. You can still play in your language if you want.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThis will change your date and hour format in Windows only.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo do that:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nOpen your Windows tab (completely left in the taskbar)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOpen Settings (\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan title=\u0022\u0022\u003Enotched wheel)\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan tit