3C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis should not happen in released software, but this is KSP so I\u0027m learning of weird new ways for software to fail as well as about orbital mechanics.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AggressiveYoghurt","CreatedById":200878,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-19T14:01:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaving the same issue, i would rather not set my entire system as a US format as it changes the date format to the wrong \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003EMM\u003C/abbr\u003E/DD/YYYY which drives me up the wall. Stock game, persists out of steam and tried rebuilding settings.cfg and setting to read-only, never happened before.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Serenity","CreatedById":179192,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-19T17:20:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223690224\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571493676\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200878\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AggressiveYoghurt\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, AggressiveYoghurt said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaving the same issue, i would rather not set my entire system as a US format as it changes the date format to the wrong \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003EMM\u003C/abbr\u003E/DD/YYYY which drives me up the wall. Stock game, persists out of steam and tried rebuilding settings.cfg and setting to read-only, never happened before.\n\